---
title: AI Agent Runtime Pipeline - Single Turn Processing
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant CUST as Customer (Audio)
    participant RTP as Media Server
    participant ASR as Streaming ASR
    participant INT as Intent Detector
    participant LLM as LLM Agent Planner
    participant TR as Tool Router
    participant PG as Policy Gateway
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant ENT as Enterprise System
    participant VAL as Output Validator
    participant TTS as Streaming TTS

    Note over CUST,TTS: STREAMING PIPELINE (Target: <800ms perceived latency)

    CUST->>RTP: Audio stream (20ms RTP frames)
    RTP->>ASR: Clean audio (WebSocket stream)
    
    Note over ASR: Partial transcripts every 100-300ms
    ASR-->>INT: Partial transcript (for pre-classification)
    ASR->>INT: Final transcript (on VAD silence boundary)
    
    INT->>LLM: Intent + slots + confidence + conversation history

    Note over LLM: Agent Planner decides: respond / tool_call / escalate

    alt Tool Call Required
        LLM->>TR: Structured tool call request
        TR->>TR: Schema validation (correct function + params)
        TR->>PG: Policy check (consent, PII, rate limit)
        PG-->>TR: APPROVED / DENIED
        
        alt Policy Approved
            TR->>API: Execute tool call
            API->>ENT: API request
            ENT-->>API: Response
            API-->>TR: Result (PII masked by compliance gateway)
            TR-->>LLM: Tool result (sanitized)
        else Policy Denied
            TR-->>LLM: Denial reason (e.g., "PII access blocked")
        end
    end

    Note over LLM: Generate response (streamed token by token)
    
    LLM->>VAL: Response text (streaming)
    
    Note over VAL: Check: PII patterns, ungrounded claims, compliance
    
    alt Validation Passed
        VAL->>TTS: Approved text (sentence chunks)
        Note over TTS: Synthesize audio in chunks (200-400ms each)
        TTS->>RTP: Audio chunks (streaming)
        RTP->>CUST: RTP audio frames
    else Validation Failed
        VAL->>LLM: Regenerate (with constraint)
    end

    Note over CUST,TTS: Total perceived latency: 400-800ms<br/>(ASR partial + LLM first token + TTS first chunk overlap)
